  <brief_title>Serum Parameter Prior and After EUS-guided Fine Needle Aspiration of the Pancreas</brief_title>
  <official_title>Serum Lipase, Amylase and CA 19-9 Prior and After EUS-guided Fine Needle Aspiration of the Pancreas</official_title>
